Class Model

java.lang.Object
src.main.java.Model
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The Model class contains all data. This data is garden width and height, plants and their data (Names, traits, descriptions, coordinates).
